sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant User as Workflow user
  participant Route as Task/Project route
  participant Hook as Live freshness hook
  participant API as GET /api/v1/tasks/updates
  participant ReadModel as Task/Project read models

  User->>Route: Opens task detail, Projects, workspace, or inbox
  Route->>Hook: Start route-scoped polling with cursor
  Hook->>API: Poll with bearer token and cursor
  API->>ReadModel: Read tenant-scoped Task, Project, and membership projections
  ReadModel-->>API: Projection snapshots and mutation positions
  API-->>Hook: Permission-safe updates and next cursor
  Hook->>Hook: Ignore stale or duplicate versions
  Hook->>Route: Trigger existing refresh callback for relevant fresh updates
  Route-->>User: Visible state refreshes without page reload
  API-->>Hook: Error, invalid cursor, or feature disabled
  Hook-->>User: Show stale, reconnecting, degraded, or manual refresh state
